    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Goblet of Shame</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Sheila Rizzo letter scores Robert Lipsyte fo divulging name of character who dies in Harry Potter and the Goblet of Firer</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Sports Editor:</p>
        <p>Shame on Robert Lipsyte for divulging the name of the character who dies in ''Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire'' (''Potter and Hilton: At Times, Morality Comes With a Broomstick,'' Aug. 6). I never dreamed that a sports columnist would kill the suspense for me and presumably thousands of other Harry Potter fans.</p>
        <p>SHEILA RIZZO  Tenafly, N.J.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
